	   <tr><td colspan=2>Equipping focus items (after lvl 34) while you summon a pet will make your pet bigger and more powerful.  There are VERY good threads on this site about how to complete the quests to obtain your focus items.  You can find these threads in the Equipment/Search area of this site.  Just do a search for mage quests.  In the list that comes up after you hit search you'll see links to the Shovel of Ponz, Torch of Alna, Stein of Ulissa, and Broom of Trilon.  Actually, you'll see links for ALL the quests mages can complete but these four are the focus items.  Good luck and good hunting :)<br><br>Aabianka Dreamstalker<br>Level 34 Mage<br>Legions of Might<br>Zebuxoruk Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
